data.description: ATTENTION!! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath Dr. Horton home is ready for its NEW FAMILY!! This home is in the popular Yowell Ranch Community and offers over 2120 sq. ft.  As you enter this home, you will be greeted by an open-concept living, dining/breakfast area that flows into the lovely kitchen equipped with all stainless-steel appliances. The kitchen offers a corner pantry. The granite countertop island is the center of attraction as the hub for family dinners and catching up with the family at the end of the day.  If you like to entertain, the open-concept is just right for you.  Retreat to the master bedroom, your happy place, in the evening. The master bedroom is on the main floor with a large size shower and walk-in closet.  An additional room and full bath on the main floor is ideal for guests. As you walk upstairs, you are greeted by a loft which is perfect for family bonding moments. Create new family memories in this additional living area.  The two additional bedrooms and full bath are located upstairs. The sought after Yowell Ranch Community offers a pool, basketball court, 2 playgrounds, and trails. This home is close to shopping, dining, and schools. So, STOP WHAT YOU ARE DOING AND COME SEE YOUR FUTURE HOME! Schedule your Showing Appointment NOW!
